I will eat a healthy diet of fruits and vegetables, with a focus on whole fruits and vegetables.  I will also include a healthy amount of nuts and seeds.  I will also limit my intake of processed foods and limit my saturated fat intake.  I will also limit my sodium intake to 200 mg per day.  I will also limit my carbohydrates to 20 grams per day.

I will also exercise regularly, at least 30 minutes per day.  I will also maintain a healthy weight, with a goal of losing 5-10 pounds per week.

Overall, I am committed to maintaining a healthy lifestyle, and I am excited to see how my plan will impact my weight loss progress..
